{"tid":498292,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[好文共賞]世界上沒有一種音樂高質/有深度過JPOP同METAL。","createTime":"2017-12-13T15:50:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-28T14:51:29.000Z","uid":139815,"like":8,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d1b81db8a1375e6a041d009d9f2179515d6cb419","tid":498292,"uid":139815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T15:50:24.000Z","msg":"我覺得沒有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n街上年輕的人只懂聽韓國和歐美的垃圾歌曲 <br />\n還有一些老餅聽支那、台灣以及香港的歌曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n在地鐵/巴士上,我會專登令耳機不塞進耳朵內,藉此將JPOP與METAL種類的音樂播出來,好讓那麼凡夫俗子知道音樂是那一回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n那些平凡人有時會走開,我想是他們有自知之明了,坐在我身邊只會顯得他們低俗,所以不與我同坐。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但還有一些低俗的90後00後,就算我專登從耳機播放出JPOP與METAL給他們聽,但他們不理會我,繼續在他們的手機上播放其他音樂,真是對牛彈琴的呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1554141136d5812fd0b2f9277d794ee8502cc72","tid":498292,"uid":15691,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T15:51:54.000Z","msg":"是但搵首jazz都輕鬆收你皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be031b0ce2424697da71233f8eacfaad041a9616","tid":498292,"uid":139815,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T15:53:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>是但搵首jazz都輕鬆收你皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n從樂理到結構上,jazz也比不上這兩個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99bb07a853706f753e7eb594ac13da7dca292db9","tid":498292,"uid":139815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T15:54:20.000Z","msg":"其實jrock也是很好的<br />\n排世界第三<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f2e69d3eef4878452e7a1041e1e6200ed6761af","tid":498292,"uid":49157,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T